ygData.messageBody:
guys why are ya listening to that crap....he said the guy wanted him to twink him to 39
you all forget the cap or something...no way a level 39 could have a 172 skill..its all BS
and what has happened to the board here...we are falling apart...anyway now that i think
about it its true that if there was no cap you would have gnomes powered to 16 and bam overmite
master tinkerers....much as i hate it ive spent too much time and money to be pushed out
of the market cause of some level 50 rich pc...now lets pull back together and get back on the
problems at hand...thx:)
